How to install the Eat&Drive
============================

1. The Eat&Drive portal was developed for Ruby 1.9.3p392, and hasn't been
   tested on other versions.

2. Run `bundler` to install all the required gems for the E&D portal.

3. Copy config/database.example.yml to config/database.yml and edit the
   file to suit your needs.

4. Run `rake db:setup`

5. E&D is good to go! An example superuser account has been created for
   you.
   
   E-mailaddress: cas@example.org
   Password:      cas
